H1: references Class

H2: Interface

!class_interface "references"

H2: Description

The {{references}} filter is used to declare a set of
references and matching documents. It can also be used to
build a table of references within a document.

The attributes supported are:

!block table
Attribute       Description
Reference       the document code
Document        the document name
Version         the document version
Status          the document status
Jump            the URL, if any
!endblock

H2: Examples

See the {{FILE:sdf.sdm}} and {{FILE:document.reg}} files within SDF's
{{FILE:sdf}} directory.

